category: X11
requires: libcogl9 libcairo-devel libgdk_pixbuf2.0-devel libglib2.0-devel libpango1.0-devel libX11-devel libXdamage-devel libXext-devel libXfixes-devel
external-source: cogl
sdesc: "GObject OpenGL library (development)"
ldesc: "Cogl is a small open source library for using 3D graphics 
hardware for rendering. The API departs from the flat state machine 
style of OpenGL and is designed to make it easy to write orthogonal 
components that can render without stepping on each others toes."
